🌤️ Weather Vision

A modern, responsive Weather Forecast Web Application that displays real-time weather information including temperature, humidity, and wind speed for any searched city.

📸 Preview

Clean gradient UI with modern weather card design.

✨ Features

🔍 Search weather by city name

🌡️ Displays current temperature

🏙️ Shows city name dynamically

💧 Humidity information

🌬️ Wind speed details

🎨 Modern gradient card design

📱 Fully responsive layout

⚡ Smooth UI experience

🛠️ Built With

HTML5

CSS3

JavaScript

Weather API (Optional if connected)

📂 Project Structure
Weather-Vision/
│
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
└── README.md
🚀 How to Run Locally

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/Ankitkumar1192/weather-vision.git
live link 

Open the project folder.

Open index.html in your browser.

🌍 How It Works

User enters a city name.

JavaScript fetches weather data from API.

Weather details update dynamically:

Temperature

Humidity

Wind Speed

City Name

🎨 UI Highlights

Gradient purple background

Rounded weather card

Minimalist search bar

Clean icon placement

Centered content layout

Balanced spacing and typography

